# QuickChat - Part 2

This project is developed for the PROG5121 Programming Assignment (Part 2).

## Features
- User registration and login
- Menu-driven console application
- Send messages
- Disregard messages
- Store messages in JSON file
- Message ID generation
- Message hash generation
- Unit testing with JUnit

## Menu Options
1. Send Messages
2. Show recently sent messages (Coming Soon)
3. Quit

## Notes
- Users must log in before sending messages
- Messages are limited based on user input
- Message hash uses first and last words (uppercase)
